              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-03-27T20:57:40.000+00:00">27 March 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Revised sections on aerosol generating procedures and theatres.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-03-23T11:44:25.000+00:00">23 March 2020</time>
